OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,FLiverpool have opened talks with
OL,7,FAndoni Iraola about becoming their new
OL,8,Fhead coach, following the sacking od
OL,9,Fhead coach Arne Slot.
OL,11,FBournemouth's former boss was quickly
OL,12,Fidentified as the primary target after
OL,13,Fthe surprise sacking on Saturday 30
OL,14,FMay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
