FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,FIt has been reported that sporting
OL,7,Fdirector Richard Hughes, who already
OL,8,Fhas a relationship with the Basque
OL,9,Fhaving appointed him three years ago
OL,10,Fwhen he was working in a similar role
OL,11,Fwith the Cherries, has made contact
OL,12,Fand is leading the talks.
OL,14,FLiverpool are keen to make a swift
OL,15,Fappointment, ideally before the start
OL,16,Fof the World Cup next week, to allow
OL,17,Fpre-season preparations to be adjusted
OL,18,Faccordingly but they insist they will
OL,19,Ffollow a proper process in order to
OL,20,Fmake the right appointment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,FAt this point there have been no
OL,7,Fapproaches to any individuals to join
OL,8,Fthe coaching staff ` it was reported
OL,9,FIraola would want to bring Cherries
OL,10,Fassistant manager Tommy Elphick with
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FThe pursuit of Iraola is in line with
OL,14,Fthe club's desire to move back towards
OL,15,Fa more aggressive, front-foot, urgent
OL,16,Fstyle of football which they lost
OL,17,Fduring Slot's second season and which
OL,18,Fultimately cost him his job.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool defender Jamie
OL,7,FCarragher feels the 43-year-old still
OL,8,Fhas plenty to prove.
OL,10,F"It looks like it's going to be Andoni
OL,11,FIraola, who is ` I think we'd all say
OL,12,F` fantastic for what he's done at
OL,13,FBournemouth," he told The Overlap Fan
OL,14,FDebate.
OL,16,F"But if you'd have said to me a few
OL,17,Fweeks ago, 'Would you sack Arne Slot
OL,18,Fand bring in Iraola?' I'd be a little
OL,19,Fbit like 'I'm not sure'.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@MO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,F"When they (big six clubs) make an
OL,7,Fappointment, I look at it and think
OL,8,F'Can I see this man winning the league
OL,9,Ffor this club?'.
OL,11,F"We had a manager who won the league.
OL,12,FThe performances last season were so
OL,13,Fpoor, I get it, I understand (why Slot
OL,14,Fwas sacked).
OL,16,F"But a manager from Bournemouth who
OL,17,Fhas never had much European experience
OL,18,Fmanaging a Champions League season,
OL,19,Fthree games a week ` that's a risk.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,F"I thought the next step for him
OL,7,F(would be to) prove he can still
OL,8,Fproduce the goods in a European season
OL,9,Fand then he'd be ready for his next
OL,10,Fmove.
OL,12,F"It almost feels like it's a year too
OL,13,Fearly."
OL,15,FCarragher's personal choice was former
OL,16,Fteam-mate Xabi Alonso, who last month
OL,17,Fjoined Chelsea but was reportedly
OL,18,Fnever high on the list of candidates
OL,19,Ffor Liverpool.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,FHowever, Carragher felt the Spaniard's
OL,7,Fvast experience made him more suited
OL,8,Fas he could have wielded more power as
OL,9,Fa manager rather than fitting into the
OL,10,Fhead coach set-up.
OL,12,F"Iraola's done a brilliant job, but
OL,13,Fit's a big jump from Bournemouth to
OL,14,FLiverpool," he added.
OL,16,F"With Alonso, you've got the playing
OL,17,Fcareer, the CV, the managers he's been
OL,18,Fmanaged by, what he did at (Bayer)
OL,19,FLeverkusen ` winning the league,
OL,20,Fgetting to a European final, playing
OL,21,Funbeaten football.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@KO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780423900
OL,3,CLiverpool open Andoni Iraola talks
OL,4,Cabout becoming their new head coach
OL,6,F"He's managed Real Madrid. I know it
OL,7,Fdidn't go well, but he's managed at
OL,8,Fthat level. That scrutiny, that
OL,9,Fpressure.
OL,11,F"If they chose Iraola above Alonso
OL,12,Fbecause of some structural preference
OL,13,F` that, for me, is very worrying for
OL,14,FLiverpool going forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
